cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.PF 

This paper is primarily focused on improving congestion control in RDMA-based datacenter networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of novel switch hardware for in-order flow deflection (cs.AR) and proposes a new approach to congestion control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper evaluates its approach through simulations and testbed measurements (cs.PF) and focuses on improving performance in datacenter networks (cs.DC).
